Package: network-sentinel
Version: 0.1.0-1
Depends: logread
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Network Sentinel <sentinel@local>
Section: net
Priority: optional
Description: Plain-English threat briefings from firewall and DNS activity.
 Reads router logs, explains events in 2-3 sentences, suggests a safe action.
 Template-based (Phase A); optional SLM via llama.cpp or proxy (Phase B).
 No automatic firewall changes.
